==============================================================

Libnotify-mozilla is subject to the terms detailed in the license
agreement accompanying it.

This Read Me file contains information about system
requirements and installation instructions.

For more info on Libnotify-mozilla, see 
https://launchpad.net/libnotify-mozilla. To submit bugs
or other feedback, see https://bugs.launchpad.net/libnotify-mozilla.


==============================================================

                      Getting Mozilla

==============================================================

For the very latest builds, see

  https://launchpad.net/libnotify-mozilla/+download


==============================================================

                    System Requirements

==============================================================


*Linux

	-The following library versions (or compatible) are
	 required: notify-send and python-indicate.
    -Thunderbird 3.0.*


==============================================================

                 Installation Instructions

==============================================================


Linux Installation Instructions
-------------------------------
        Proceed like many other addon installation. Please, 
        make sure you have notify-send and python-indicate installed.
